Webhook Delivery System
Overview

This project implements a Webhook Delivery System that allows clients to register webhook endpoints and receive event notifications. The system ensures reliable delivery using a queue and background workers.

The architecture separates the API service from the delivery workers to improve scalability and reliability.

Architecture

Client
↓
API Service (Webhook Management + Event Ingestion)
↓
Message Queue
↓
Delivery Workers
↓
External Webhook Endpoints

Tech Stack

Python – API and worker services

FastAPI / Flask – REST API

Redis / RabbitMQ – Message Queue

PostgreSQL – Database

Docker & Docker Compose – Containerization

