API service

Worker service

Redis / RabbitMQ

Mock receiver server

API Endpoints
Register Webhook
POST /webhooks

Example request body:

{
  "url": "http://mock_receiver:5000/webhook"
}
Send Event
POST /events

Example request:

{
  "event": "user_created",
  "data": {
    "user_id": 123
  }
}

The event will be pushed to the queue and delivered asynchronously by the worker.

Testing the Webhook

A mock receiver server is included to simulate an external webhook endpoint.

It will print received events in the logs.

Running Services

